---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service | Boomy Marketing Agency"
  description="Boomy Marketing Agency terms of service. Read the terms governing your use of our website and services."
  canonical="https://boomymarketing.com/terms/"
>
  <section class="page-hero" style="min-height:40vh;">
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a><span>/</span><span aria-current="page">Terms of Service</span>
      </nav>
      <h1>Terms of <span class="gradient-text">Service</span></h1>
      <p>Last updated: April 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background:var(--bg-deep);padding:80px 5%;">
    <div style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;color:var(--text-sec);line-height:1.8;font-size:.97rem;">
      <h2 style="color:var(--text-primary);font-size:1.4rem;margin-bottom:16px;">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:24px;">By accessing or using the Boomy Marketing Agency website and services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use our services.</p>

      <h2 style="color:var(--text-primary);font-size:1.4rem;margin-bottom:16px;">2. Services</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:24px;">Boomy Marketing Agency provides digital marketing services including SEO, paid advertising, social media management, web design, and AI-powered marketing solutions. Specific terms for client engagements are governed by individual service agreements.</p>

      <h2 style="color:var(--text-primary);font-size:1.4rem;margin-bottom:16px;">3. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:24px;">All content on this website, including text, graphics, logos, and software, is the property of Boomy Marketing Agency and is protected by applicable intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce or distribute content without written permission.</p>

      <h2 style="color:var(--text-primary);font-size:1.4rem;margin-bottom:16px;">4. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:24px;">Boomy Marketing Agency shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of our website or services. Our total liability shall not exceed the fees paid for the specific service giving rise to the claim.</p>

      <h2 style="color:var(--text-primary);font-size:1.4rem;margin-bottom:16px;">5. Governing Law</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:24px;">These terms are governed by the laws of the Province of Ontario, Canada. Any disputes shall be resolved in the courts of Toronto, Ontario.</p>

      <h2 style="color:var(--text-primary);font-size:1.4rem;margin-bottom:16px;">6. Contact</h2>
      <p>Boomy Marketing Agency — 240 Richmond St W, Toronto, ON M5V 1V6, Canada<br />
      Email: <a href="mailto:care@boomymarketing.com" style="color:var(--accent-orange)">care@boomymarketing.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
